ana US House seat|url=https://nbcmontana.com/news/local/williams-launches-new-bid-for-montana-us-house-seat|agency=Associated Press|publisher=KECI|date=April 5, 2019|accessdate=April 5, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Endorsements===\n{{Endorsements box\n|title=Steve Bullock\n|list=\n;Federal officials \n*[[Chris Lu]], former [[United States Deputy Secretary of Labor]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/ChrisLu44/status/1237004773552947203|title=Excited to see Steve Bullock jump in. This is a critical race to help us take back the Senate. Please consider making a contribution. I just did.|work=Twitter |last=Lu |first=Chris|date=March 9, 2020 |accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Richard Blumenthal]], U.S. Senator [D-CT]<ref>Blumenthal sent out an email to supporters soliciting donations to Bullock.</ref>\n*[[Kirsten Gillibrand]], U.S. Senator [D-NY]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/SenGillibrand/status/1237017906011164672|title=.@stevebullockmt has proven to be one of the most effective governors in the country\u2014now, he's running for Senate in Montana! Are you in to take back the Senate from Mitch McConnell? |work=Twitter |last=Gillibrand |first=Kirsten |date=March 9, 2020 |accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Amy Klobuchar]], U.S. Senator [D-MN]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/amyklobuchar/status/1237515818797338627|title=MT Gov Steve Bullock is a fighter. He understands the needs of working families & believes in investing in education & job training. It's great to know he will continue this fight in his run for Senate (@Bullock4Senate) & will help flip the Senate blue!|work=Twitter |last=Klobuchar |first=Amy |date=March 9, 2020 |accessdate=March 9, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Chris Murphy]], U.S. Senator [D-CT]<ref>https://twitter.com/ChrisMurphyCT/status/1255222362196377600</ref>\n*[[Jon Tester]], U.S. Senator [D-MT]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/jontester/status/1237060270859706370 |title=Washington needs more Montana common sense, and I know my frien